<i>noun</i>: 청교도 [청교도] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>청교도 [청교도]</dt><br>
<dd>Puritanism</dd><br>
<dd>16세기 후반에 영국 국교회에 반항하여 생겼으며 모든 쾌락을 죄로 여긴 개신교의 한 교파.</dd><br>
<dd>A religious sect of the Protestant Church that formed in opposition to the Church of England in the late 16th century, which considered all pleasure as sin.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>